nt gear with recent loot the tool tips frequently disappear by players joining and dropping from the tavern further adding to my frustration.The gameplay itself has remained largely unchanged aside from a pointless crafting system, texture pop in and balance issues.If you own the original there is little to no point in purchasing this new version and strongly suggest you avoid it until some large changes are made and maybe not even then. Hopefully Dungeon Defenders 2 won’t leave me with such a bitter experience."
